snippet.title: GAME MADE IN WEEK - Cat Architect Trailer - Play For Free!
snippet.description:
Link: https://shinseyy.itch.io/cat-architect

Small game I made for Game Jam #ZostanWDomuRobGry in a week. It's a cute game about rebuildding world with your cat friend. Upgrade your crane, watch out for dangers and finish the building! Sure nothing wrong will happen...
Game was made in Construct 3
